[
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.1",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "The words of king Lemuel, the prophecy that his mother taught him.",
    "hash": "7382188ba5d65b829cf59f527abd5a45e9b44d01d674063a08cd85629cb46c89"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.2",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 2,
    "text": "What, my son? and what, the son of my womb? and what, the son of my vows?",
    "hash": "fb57543c5355b2f33f1f4dfd5bd19d1518fe74418dd0a91fd62efac5b492ba91"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.3",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "Give not thy strength unto women, nor thy ways to that which destroyeth kings.",
    "hash": "134102ce424ba62a7c104f104fa1eafeab025f59dc27b90f964c0343f40857c2"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.4",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "{It is} not for kings, O Lemuel, {it is} not for kings to drink wine; nor for princes strong drink:",
    "hash": "ab14317c9d7ed9427dd9831947082df0de258d8f345614514c5e5c6e61c8761d"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.5",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 5,
    "text": "Lest they drink, and forget the law, and pervert the judgment of any of the afflicted. {prevert: Heb. alter} {of any...: Heb. of all the sons of affliction}",
    "hash": "97d613056bdaa7fe77515ae844baf13f838c704a1cf224cdc778e4ec6acc1182"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.6",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 6,
    "text": "Give strong drink unto him that is ready to perish, and wine unto those that be of heavy hearts. {of...: Heb. bitter of soul}",
    "hash": "3b771ffdd34bc8f77c58123ab901e368842690a4c22eb85f593326e8848aa913"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.7",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 7,
    "text": "Let him drink, and forget his poverty, and remember his misery no more.",
    "hash": "7d98764942d692d44746d2078dee49e35689bebd6b4f5c2d6b1fd3bc0e6b5377"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.8",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 8,
    "text": "Open thy mouth for the dumb in the cause of all such as are appointed to destruction. {such...: Heb. the sons of destruction}",
    "hash": "ca5fc307564a2d5d554b6246ccc039b31056b886e4a13e4aadbb2c7ba69ae649"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.9",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 9,
    "text": "Open thy mouth, judge righteously, and plead the cause of the poor and needy.",
    "hash": "5b471c169a8d62d96392c5c688be31f1042a74131d923cdfbb000d0d3460f8c3"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.10",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 10,
    "text": "Who can find a virtuous woman? for her price {is} far above rubies.",
    "hash": "0229dd61359a41169da625d26b457f2aae58aab51246e9e15506989a978d10b2"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.11",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 11,
    "text": "The heart of her husband doth safely trust in her, so that he shall have no need of spoil.",
    "hash": "946bb0d21416c011cf91f494d0476ff312ba03840172b082195846202895fdd8"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.12",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 12,
    "text": "She will do him good and not evil all the days of her life.",
    "hash": "9a1f7792db1e7418f70b42a14ba9ba28cac346ea5d69b7be3516bf7e286320d1"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.13",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 13,
    "text": "She seeketh wool, and flax, and worketh willingly with her hands.",
    "hash": "31d202f743a3137ee1ef1cf6734f18ca8b27677230b716c58db3fb7c82687231"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.14",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 14,
    "text": "She is like the merchants' ships; she bringeth her food from afar.",
    "hash": "e2afd4949abd2624dba6ab39c854fdf647c3db545d416bf47890eb9d8278891f"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.15",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 15,
    "text": "She riseth also while it is yet night, and giveth meat to her household, and a portion to her maidens.",
    "hash": "172ef6fa2b93427d78d6e4f2204865dea3ec424b23aa0bef4c68939e5b7bf900"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.16",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "She considereth a field, and buyeth it: with the fruit of her hands she planteth a vineyard. {buyeth: Heb. taketh}",
    "hash": "e27b87e77a3433438abf9eb6c93e0df3ffa53eb650c3045585615fd343bae97e"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.17",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "She girdeth her loins with strength, and strengtheneth her arms.",
    "hash": "3d88822fea8ead5e93034dae97e28bdeac1dce178794cfe4efd7b218a1d9872b"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.18",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "She perceiveth that her merchandise {is} good: her candle goeth not out by night. {She...: Heb. She tasteth}",
    "hash": "411fa5a0f7e5cb869c305fe598a00671136d96c51e6375edb6dc298131906ba8"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.19",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "She layeth her hands to the spindle, and her hands hold the distaff.",
    "hash": "d439895ed0e8798b783d4bd82bb33db12efdf04d229f55de2393eee92626386a"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.20",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "She stretcheth out her hand to the poor; yea, she reacheth forth her hands to the needy. {She...: Heb. She spreadeth}",
    "hash": "199cb8d53292fb6e70ad4a44ebd979b46ea82499d7e322d742239ee0b2151729"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.21",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "She is not afraid of the snow for her household: for all her household {are} clothed with scarlet. {scarlet: or, double garments}",
    "hash": "30b403fee2a118cb53a6a76dda623154d402079415880820f2bc0b4b849c61ba"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.22",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "She maketh herself coverings of tapestry; her clothing {is} silk and purple.",
    "hash": "b86e804a0589e6bff309ad55381be1eb3425ae9e6c314eea97ff791188c7b3ba"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.23",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "Her husband is known in the gates, when he sitteth among the elders of the land.",
    "hash": "b87155fc0f540b1783fd173975f6c56d55710c23d8741297ea217d6b9c88e263"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.24",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "She maketh fine linen, and selleth {it}; and delivereth girdles unto the merchant.",
    "hash": "dfb53178a58e05c9ab404a767988b3936c2e481ef076ad4a0ba2b80b1a978f34"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.25",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "Strength and honour {are} her clothing; and she shall rejoice in time to come.",
    "hash": "7a6702b3e014114acafbd28188e0d8644ac8d874cbc6c9713d27b20fd2a94793"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.26",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 26,
    "text": "She openeth her mouth with wisdom; and in her tongue {is} the law of kindness.",
    "hash": "f3a29cb5b499ed38172e8ceea0d498a7f0ba304a094c1bff9d9b080ca77c4602"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.27",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 27,
    "text": "She looketh well to the ways of her household, and eateth not the bread of idleness.",
    "hash": "5f80d33196752c52cc36bccf03e7933a9fb63d41e265fad1035c89b1997db03b"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.28",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 28,
    "text": "Her children arise up, and call her blessed; her husband {also}, and he praiseth her.",
    "hash": "a168dac9bebaedd89f4b45ce17c2e125419c0316a3707d6051d340641ebcef9c"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.29",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 29,
    "text": "Many daughters have done virtuously, but thou excellest them all. {have...: or, have gotten riches}",
    "hash": "07b4eadb7e585c0ad9a489f17aba7cd04b55975f83e190949ad15076d5f75323"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.30",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 30,
    "text": "Favour {is} deceitful, and beauty {is} vain: {but} a woman {that} feareth the LORD, she shall be praised.",
    "hash": "05f00f2212945e70a12e2ebc5d2663956c7c17255c696f8d43f9021e6779e2d1"
  },
  {
    "id": "PRO.31.31",
    "book": "Proverbs",
    "bookNum": 20,
    "bookAbbrev": "PRO",
    "chapter": 31,
    "verse": 31,
    "text": "Give her of the fruit of her hands; and let her own works praise her in the gates.",
    "hash": "e585ce5044a925630728c6e263449317b7d260eb024ef566634145f555aa818d"
  }
]